> ### Name: bg
> ### Title: Breusch-Godfrey test [BG test]
> ### Aliases: bg
> 
> ### ** Examples
> 
> model <- lm(real_gdp ~ imp + exp + poil + eurkzt + tonia_rate, data = macroKZ)
> bg(model)
          Breusch-Godfrey test for serial correlation of order up to 1           

Residuals are not autocorrelated. 
